"""Parse Microsoft 365 Unified Audit Log (UAL) CSV exports into a SQLite
database for digital-forensic / business-email-compromise investigations.

Each row of every CSV export is preserved verbatim, the JSON ``auditData``
blob is stored both raw (byte-for-byte) and in canonical form, and a wide
set of BEC-relevant fields are promoted into indexed columns for fast
querying.  Re-ingesting the same data is safe: full-row SHA-256 hashes are
used as the deduplication key.
"""

